Package: dghrank
Title: Construct Draper-Gittoes-Helkey Rankings of Institutions
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: c(person("Daniel", "Helkey", email = "dhelkey@ucsc.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
				person("David", "Draper", role = "ctb",
					email = "draper@ucsc.edu"),
				person("Jessica", "Liu", role = "ctb",
					email = "jbliu@stanford.edu"),
				person("Lucy", "Greenberg", role = "ctb",
					email = "LGreenberg@vtoxford.org"),
				person("Daniel", "Kirsner", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides functions for ranking institions with respect to binary outcome performance. Rankings are computed according to Draper-Gittoes-Helkey (2018), which extends Draper-Gittoes (2004) methodology. Functions are provided to generate composite scores. Main fitting function (fitBabyMonitor) intended for CPQCC/VON usage, but fast functions are provided for Bayesian linear and probit regression.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
